<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink369">
<l>vaḷamalar tatainta vaṇṭupaṭu naṟumpoḻiṉ</l>
<l>muḷainirai muṟuva loruttiyoṭu nerunaṟ</l>
<l>kuṟinī ceytaṉai yeṉpa valarē</l>
<l>kurava nīḷciṉai yaṟaiyum</l>
<l>paruva mākkuyiṟ kauvaiyiṟ peritē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>They say that yesterday you had a tryst with a girl, </l>
<l>whose smile resembles sprouts in the fragrant grove, </l>
<l>teeming with luxuriant flowers, swarmed by bees. </l>
<l>And the gossip is louder </l> 
<l>than the calls of dark cuckoos of the [spring] season,</l>
<l>singing on the long Kurava branches. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
